@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
<hr />
    <p>Lazy Sausages values your privacy. This policy explains how we handle your information when you use our finance app.</p>

<h3>Information We Collect</h3>

    <p>We collect only the information needed to provide our services—such as account details you enter, transaction data you choose to track, and basic usage information that helps us improve the app.</p>

<h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>

    <p>Your information is used to display and manage your finances inside the app. We may also use aggregated, anonymized data to improve features and ensure the app runs smoothly.</p>

<h3>Sharing Your Information</h3>

    <p>We do not sell your personal data. Information may only be shared with trusted service providers who help us operate the app, and only when necessary.</p>

<h3>Security</h3>

    <p>We *totally* take steps to protect your information through encryption and secure storage, but no system is completely risk-free.</p>

<h3>Your Choices</h3>

    <p>You can access, update, or delete your data within the app at any time. If you delete your account, your stored data will be deleted from our servers within a reasonable timeframe.</p>

<h3>Changes to This Policy</h3>

    <p>We may update this policy. If changes are significant, we’ll notify you. If you still aren't notified, blame Maripuu.</p>

<h3>Contact Us</h3>

    <p>If you have questions about your privacy, contact us.</p>
